text: Pugvin Mys () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Seyvinskoye Rural Settlement, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 64 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 45 km west from Gayny. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gaynsky District
title: Pugvin Mys
